"Change Set:		8424Compression-ul.10Compression-ul.10:- replace sends of #ifNotNilDo: to #ifNotNil:, #ifNil:ifNotNilDo: to #ifNil:ifNotNil:, #ifNotNilDo:ifNil: to #ifNotNil:ifNil:"!!GZipReadStream class methodsFor: 'fileIn/Out' stamp: 'ul 12/12/2009 14:11'!viewContents: fullFileName	"Open the decompressed contents of the .gz file with the given name.  This method is only required for the registering-file-list of Squeak 3.3a and beyond, but does no harm in an earlier system"	(FileStream readOnlyFileNamed: fullFileName) ifNotNil:		[:aStream | aStream viewGZipContents]! !